<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='300000' id='t-300000'>I can't verify that fully, but it does not matter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='302000' id='t-302000'>There is your environmental problem solved, by the way, guys:</span>
