<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308000' id='t-308000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313000' id='t-313000'>What Ataturk realized actually is two very fundamental things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='316000' id='t-316000'>Which is that, actually, first one,</span>
