 5:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337000' id='t-337000'>But the first thing is that all value is subjective.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='341000' id='t-341000'>Second point is that persuasion is often better than compulsion.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344000' id='t-344000'>These funny signs that flash your speed at you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='346000' id='t-346000'>some of the new ones, on the bottom right,</span>
