<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='431000' id='t-431000'>So, the modern equivalent would of course be this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433000' id='t-433000'>(Laughter)</span>
