</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447000' id='t-447000'>If you think about it, Shakerism was a proto-environmental movement.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='450000' id='t-450000'>Adam Smith talks about 18th century America,</span>
