 8:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469000' id='t-469000'>What's also interesting, if you look at products</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471000' id='t-471000'>that have a high component</span>
