<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509000' id='t-509000'>Now, we basically have to change our views slightly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512000' id='t-512000'>There is a basic view that real value involves making things,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='515000' id='t-515000'>involves labor. It involves engineering.</span>
